sub_title: Expert in energy efficient lighting strategies for businesses
summary:
My experience with smart technical solutions started in 2006 at DuPont and continued in Philips Lighting later known as Signify, where I helped my industrial customers to optimize their production costs via complex energy saving projects. Most of the industry leaders aim to reduce their carbon footprint and energy saving naturally becomes a part of their sustainability strategy, where I am happy to support them.

With no harm to production process and often with no extra capital expenses, hand in hand with the customers, we have implemented energy efficient lighting solutions in almost every industrial segment - from warehousing to food, chemical, automotive and mining.
